      <div class="col-12 text-center" style="z-index: 10000;">
        <p class="lead">Researchers across the continent are working together to understand the dynamics of lion populations using LINC- the Lion Identification Network of Collaborators- as a non-invasive tool for tracking, identifying and monitoring African lions. <p><%= link_to 'Learn More >', page_path('about/linc') %></p>
