        <h1 class="text-center" style="color:white">What is LINC?</h1>
        <p class="lead lead-large lead-small text-center">LINC is an open source application comprised of an online database where researchers can upload and manage data on lions in their own study areas and identify unknown lions using LINC’s embedded artificial intelligence (AI) recognition technology. LINC also enables researchers to more easily share information with other lion researchers, promoting international and inter-organisational collaboration, thereby increasing the chances of detecting connections between lion populations.
        </p>
